This paper deals with the use of an ensemble of classifiers to improve classification accuracy. The paper uses Genetical Algorithms to evolve the classifiers and measure the structural diversity of the ensemble. This is a common topic in the field of machine learning and falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
